  "locale": "cn",
  "beats": [
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_001",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_001.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「咦，和树？还没回来吗？",
        "难道你等着我吗？」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_002",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_002.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「辛苦了！我送你到门口吧。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_003",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_003.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「是吗？那明天见！」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_004",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_004.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「咦？有什么忘记的东西吗？」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          "说出关键词，进入催眠状态。"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAZU_009_NUKE004_001",
        "file": null
      },
      "lines": [
        "「可以。你在晚餐时间之前，躺在床上休息一下。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          ""
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_005",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_005.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「晚餐……在被叫到之前，躺在床上……」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAZU_009_NUKE004_002",
        "file": null
      },
      "lines": [
        "「听到门关上的声音后，就会回到平常的心态。我想和树已经回来了……」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          ""
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_006",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_006.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哎？喝的东西呢？」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          "说出关键词，进入催眠状态。"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAZU_009_NUKE004_003",
        "file": null
      },
      "lines": [
        "「可以。和树已经回家了，我打算自己完成剩下的作业。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          ""
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木翼",
      "voice": {
        "id": "TUBA_009_NUKE004_007",
        "file": "voice/tuba_009_nuke004_007.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「回家……作业，一个人完成……」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAZU_009_NUKE004_004",
        "file": null
      },
      "lines": [
        "「在晚餐时间之前，我会一直待在房间里。",
        ""
      ]
    }
